originalText.text: As a trainer and twenty five year veteran of the Fitness industry, it was clear when I met Garnett that he was a standout presence in the gym.  Along with his elite martial art skills and strength and conditioning expertise, it is his ability as a communicator that sets him apart.   His unique capacity to meet a client where they are and find the best path forward, is key to their success and to his own.  His professional development offerings teach these skills, which are arguably more important than physical education, to client retention. Garnett’s Professional program delivers this typically missing piece to continuing education in the Fitness industry. High recommend!

originalText.text: Garnett is a highly technical and thoughtful trainer.   Really enjoyed working on mobility and the preparation leading to explosive activity.  Lots of technical detail work.  Excellent trainer.

originalText.text: I trained with Garnett for three years and little did I know it would turn into a mentorship as I am now a trainer. His dedication towards physical empowerment and mental health is what initially attracted me in his method as well as our shared love of martial arts and how to best optimize our bodies for life. He excels in listening and finding the right communication style that will be best heard and will motivate you during highs and more so lows. I am thankful for the knowledge, guidance and progress provided by our training sessions and will look to pay it forward!

originalText.text:
Garnett is dope,

I’ve worked with garnett for over 10 years, it has helped me in my life as a professional fighter, and as a human being

Not only did I get in the best shape but I was mentally prepared for anything  life through my way. Honestly garnett is a great coach but where he really shines is his ability to communicate and in a way that I understand, so I can get the best results possible.

He himself is efficient mental martial artist who is dedicated to his craft of helping other people get better. I highly recommend garnett for anyone who is trying to achieve self mastery.

originalText.text: Training with Garnett for about a month has been an amazing experience! He is a wonderful trainer who is very knowledgeable and passionate about what he does and it is shown through his instruction. His instruction is very clear and he has a solution for every challenge I may come across when working out or boxing. I have been able to improve my technique and feel stronger than ever thanks to the work I’ve been doing with Garnett. He takes time to understand where you are at and tailors the workout to fit your needs and capabilities. Looking forward to continuing training with Garnett and highly recommend him!
